---
import IconFileText from '~icons/ph/file-text-duotone'
import IconStorefront from '~icons/ph/storefront-duotone'
import IconUsers from '~icons/ph/users-three-duotone'
import IconQuestion from '~icons/ph/question-duotone'
---

<section id="servicos" class="py-16 bg-white relative">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="text-center md:text-left mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">Saúde e praticidade</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl">O que você precisar, na hora que precisar. Nossos principais serviços pensados para facilitar sua vida e cuidar do seu bem-estar.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <a href="/lojas" class="group relative flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-8 hover:bg-red-50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-slate-100 ring-1 ring-slate-100 hover:ring-red-200">
        <div>
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200 text-red-600 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <IconFileText class="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-red-700 transition-colors">Envie sua Receita</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Mande uma foto da sua receita médica pelo WhatsApp e nós separamos tudo.
          </p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <a href="/lojas" class="group relative flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-8 hover:bg-red-50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-slate-100 ring-1 ring-slate-100 hover:ring-red-200">
        <div>
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200 text-red-600 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <IconStorefront class="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-red-700 transition-colors">Nossas Lojas</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Descubra qual loja física Dutra Farma está mais perto de você no Litoral.
          </p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <a href="/lojas" class="group relative flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-8 hover:bg-red-50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-slate-100 ring-1 ring-slate-100 hover:ring-red-200">
        <div>
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200 text-red-600 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <IconUsers class="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-red-700 transition-colors">Trabalhe Conosco</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Faça parte da nossa equipe e ajude a cuidar das pessoas em nossa região.
          </p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <a href="/lojas" class="group relative flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-8 hover:bg-red-50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-slate-100 ring-1 ring-slate-100 hover:ring-red-200">
        <div>
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200 text-red-600 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <IconQuestion class="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-red-700 transition-colors">Dúvidas Frequentes</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Ficou com alguma dúvida sobre entregas ou formas de pagamento?
          </p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
